  "title": "BMS Estimator (Tender Submission/Cost Estimation) LT85",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Study and understand BMS tender/ project specifications and requirements</li><li>Work closely with sales team to provide accurate costings and proposals</li><li>Prepare documents for tender submission/clarifications</li><li>Source/liaise/negotiate with suppliers and vendors on quotations and requirements</li><li>Maintain good relationships with subcontractors/vendors/clients</li><li>Perform site measurements/attend tender clarifications/interview as and when required</li><li>Any other relevant job duties as assigned</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements</strong></p><ul><li>Degree/Diploma in Engineering/Building</li><li>Experience in ACMV industry, knowledge in BMS and ACMV is a must</li><li>Able to understand technical drawings and requirements</li><li>Min 3 years experience as estimator </li><li>Able to work well under pressure to meet tight deadlines</li><li>Strong communication and negotiation skills</li></ul><p><br />HOW TO APPLY:</p><p>Interested applicants, kindly send your resume in MS WORD format to leo.tang(at)trustrecruit.com.sg</p><p>We regret only shortlisted candidates will be notified.</p><p>Important Note: Trust Recruit Pte Ltd is committed to safeguarding your personal data in accordance with the Personal Data Protection Act (PDPA).</p><p>Please read our privacy statement on our corporate website www.trustrecruit.com.sg.</p><p>Trust Recruit Pte Ltd</p><p>EA License No: 19C9950</p><p>EA Personnel: Tang For Farn (Leo)</p><p>EA Personnel Reg No: R24121981</p>",
